=== 筹备 ===
2012年1月31日，[[20世紀福克斯|20世紀福克斯]]公布其部門—福克斯2000，對[[約翰·葛林|約翰·葛林]]的小說《[[生命中的美好缺憾|生命中的美好缺憾]]》改編成為電影有選擇的權利<ref name="deahl">{{cite news |first=Rachel |last=Deahl |date=2012-01-31 |title=Fox Options John Green's 'Fault in Our Stars' |url=http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/childrens/childrens-industry-news/article/50442-fox-options-john-green-s-fault-in-our-stars.html |magazine=[[Publishers_Weekly|Publishers Weekly]] |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archive-date=2018-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181212120014/https://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/childrens/childrens-industry-news/article/50442-fox-options-john-green-s-fault-in-our-stars.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。製片人[[懷克·戈弗雷|懷克·戈弗雷]]被設定與[[馬蒂·寶雲|馬蒂·寶雲]]使用他{{link-en|美峰娛樂|Temple Hill Entertainment}}的橫幅來製作電影<ref>{{cite news|last1=Abrams|first1=Rachel|title=Fox 2000 options ‘Fault in Our Stars’|url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/fox-2000-options-fault-in-our-stars-1118049583/|accessdate=2014-08-10|publisher=variety.com|date=2012-02-01|archive-date=2014-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813013543/http://variety.com/2012/film/news/fox-2000-options-fault-in-our-stars-1118049583/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年2月19日，導演[[乔什·波恩|喬許·布恩]]獲聘作為電影的方向指導<ref name=Director>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|last2=Lewis|first2=Andy|title='The Fault in Our Stars' Movie Lands Director|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fault-stars-movie-lands-director-422485|accessdate=2014-08-10|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2013-02-19|archive-date=2018-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630133101/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fault-stars-movie-lands-director-422485|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及聘請{{link-en|史葛．紐斯塔德|Scott Neustadter}}和[[米高．H．韋伯|米高．H．韋伯]]來把小說改編成為電影劇本，作為繼羅薩琳 (Rosaline)之後，曾在[[20世紀福克斯|20世紀福克斯]]效力的第二位改編作家<ref name="Director" /><ref>{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|title=Fox 2000 Sets Neustadter & Weber To Adapt ‘The Fault In Our Stars’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/03/fox-2000-sets-neustadter-weber-to-adapt-the-fault-in-our-stars/|accessdate=2014-08-10|publisher=deadline.com|date=2012-03-28|archive-date=2014-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716042825/http://www.deadline.com/2012/03/fox-2000-sets-neustadter-weber-to-adapt-the-fault-in-our-stars/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 選角 ===
2012年11月，根據小說作者[[約翰·葛林|約翰·葛林]]有[[Twitter|Twitter]]網站上表示有意找[[梅·惠特曼|梅·惠特曼]]飾演Hazel Grace Lancaster<ref name="#2">{{cite news|last1=Lamoureux|first1=Jen|title=‘The Fault in Our Stars’ casting: Who should play Hazel?|url=http://www.hypable.com/2012/11/19/the-fault-in-our-stars-casting-who-should-play-hazel/|accessdate=2014-08-10|publisher=hypable.com|date=2012-11-19|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006104926/http://www.hypable.com/2012/11/19/the-fault-in-our-stars-casting-who-should-play-hazel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年2月，該公司公布[[海莉·史坦菲德|海莉·史坦菲德]]與[[莎蓮·活莉|莎蓮·活莉]]都不獲選，但成為眼中女主角的人選<ref name="Director" />。2013年3月19日，《[[娛樂週刊|娛樂週刊]]》報導指[[莎蓮·活莉|莎蓮·活莉]]將飾演Hazel Grace Lancaster的一角，而當時莎蓮·活莉正拍攝《[[分歧者·異類叛逃|分歧者·異類叛逃]]》<ref name=casting1>{{cite web|author=Sara Vilkomerson|title=Shailene Woodley offered lead role for 'The Fault in Our Stars'|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/03/19/shailene-woodley-fault-in-our-stars/|publisher=''Entertainment Weekly''|date=2013-03-19|accessdate=2013-03-19|archive-date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218082825/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/03/19/shailene-woodley-fault-in-our-stars/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。導演說：「我們看過接近250位女演員為角色的演繹，我看過當中的50位，在莎蓮的10至15秒試鐘裡，我知道她就是Hazel，只有她有鏡頭前讓我首次真正的看到Hazel。她手握著她的劇本，和只有她的眼睛偷看過他們<ref name="casting1" /><ref>{{cite web|title=The Fault in Our Stars - Movie Production Notes|url=http://www.cinemareview.com/production.asp?prodid=18394|publisher=CinemaReview.com|accessdate=2014-08-13|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925201708/http://www.cinemareview.com/production.asp?prodid=18394|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Fault in Our Stars — Movie Production Notes|url=http://www.cinemareview.com/production.asp?prodid=18394|publisher=CinemaReview.com|accessdate=2014-08-13|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925201708/http://www.cinemareview.com/production.asp?prodid=18394|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」5月10日，[[安塞爾·埃爾格特|安塞爾·埃爾格特]]為Hazel的戀人Augustus Waters進行試鏡<ref name=casting2>{{cite news|last1=Sneider|first1=Jeff|title=‘Divergent’ Star Ansel Elgort to Join Shailene Woodley in ‘The Fault In Our Stars’|url=http://www.thewrap.com/movies/column-post/divergent-star-ansel-elgort-join-shailene-woodley-fault-our-stars-90881/|accessdate=2014-08-11|publisher=thewrap.com|date=2013-05-10|archive-date=2018-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630105630/https://www.thewrap.com/movies/column-post/divergent-star-ansel-elgort-join-shailene-woodley-fault-our-stars-90881/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月23日，[[蘿拉·鄧恩|蘿拉·鄧恩]]加入劇組飾演Hazel的母親Frannie Lancaster，以及[[納特·沃爾夫|納特·沃爾夫]]飾演Augustus的失明好友Issac<ref name=casting3>{{cite news |first=Sara |last=Vilkomerson |date=2013-07-23 |title=Nat Wolff cast as Isaac in 'The Fault in Our Stars' |magazine=Entertainment Weekly |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/07/23/nat-wolff-fault-in-our-stars-isaac |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006144725/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/07/23/nat-wolff-fault-in-our-stars-isaac/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。沃爾夫跟《{{link-en|哈芬登郵報Live|HuffPost Live}}》指「這是很令人興奮的事，我感到非常幸運，事實上我跟這班具天賦的人們一起合作—我的意思是，這就是為何我在電影中出色的原因之一，這就是原因<ref name="#1"/>。」8月14日，[[山姆·特拉梅爾|山姆·特拉梅爾]]試演作為Hazel的父親Micheal Lancaster<ref name=casting4>{{cite news|last1=Sneider|first1=Jeff|title=‘True Blood's’ Sam Trammell Joins Shailene Woodley in ‘The Fault in Our Stars’|url=http://www.thewrap.com/movies/column-post/true-bloods-sam-trammell-joins-shailene-woodley-fault-our-stars-exclusive-110821/|accessdate=2013-08-11|publisher=thewrap.com|date=2013-08-14|archive-date=2018-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630105306/https://www.thewrap.com/movies/column-post/true-bloods-sam-trammell-joins-shailene-woodley-fault-our-stars-exclusive-110821/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在8月29日，小說的作者[[約翰·格林|約翰·格林]]公布[[麥克·柏比葛利亞|麥克·柏比葛利亞]]將飾演Patrick一角<ref name=casting5>{{cite news|last1=Green|first1=John|title=Mike Birbiglia will play Patrick|url=https://twitter.com/realjohngreen/statuses/372831664281772032|accessdate=2014-08-29|publisher=twitter.com|date=2013-08-28|archive-date=2014-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140915130209/https://twitter.com/realjohngreen/statuses/372831664281772032|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他亦於9月6日在[[推特|推特]]發文公布指[[威廉·達福|威廉·達福]]將會飾演Peter van Houten<ref name=casting6>{{cite news|last1=Bahr|first1=Lindsey|title=Willem Dafoe cast as Peter Van Houten in 'The Fault in Our Stars'|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/09/06/willem-dafoe-the-fault-in-our-stars/|accessdate=2014-08-29|publisher=ew.com|date=2013-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006130136/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/09/06/willem-dafoe-the-fault-in-our-stars/|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

在這些消息公布前，小說的作者[[約翰·格林|約翰·格林]]曾發文指，若[[梅·惠特曼|梅·惠特曼]]飾演Hazel的話會讓他感到高興<ref name="#2"/>，然而在2013年2月，有猜測指[[海莉·史坦菲德|海莉·史坦菲德]]與[[莎蓮·活莉|莎蓮·活莉]]當中一人將會被考慮成為主角的人選<ref name="Director" />。

小說的作者約翰·格林亦有於電影中作[[友情客串|友情客串]]；然而他的場景於電影中被裁掉，片段只於電影的DVD及[[藍光影碟|藍光影碟]]發布版本中出現。在裁掉的場景中，格林飾演小女孩的父親，那小女孩在機場等候期間問及Hazel的氧氣喉管的事<ref>{{cite web |author=Jaimie Etkin |url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/jaimieetkin/heres-your-first-look-at-john-greens-the-fault-in-our-stars |title=Here's Your First Look At John Green's "The Fault In Our Stars" Cameo |publisher=Buzzfeed.com |accessdate=2014-06-06 |date=2014-05-27 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111172504/http://www.buzzfeed.com/jaimieetkin/heres-your-first-look-at-john-greens-the-fault-in-our-stars |dead-url=no }}</ref>，格林說：「他們裁掉（場景）是因為這對電影來說完全沒有必要，這個對我來說太可怕了<ref name=vulture-interview>{{cite news|last1=Vineyard|first1=Jennifer|title=Summer Movie Preview 2014: John Green on The Fault in Our Stars and the Magic of Shailene Woodley|url=http://www.vulture.com/2014/04/john-green-interview-fault-in-our-stars-shailene-woodley.html|accessdate=2014-08-29|publisher=vulture.com|date=2014-04-29|archive-date=2015-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926100133/http://www.vulture.com/2014/04/john-green-interview-fault-in-our-stars-shailene-woodley.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」

=== 拍攝 ===
主要拍攝在2013年8月26日於[[美國|美國]][[賓夕凡尼亞州|賓夕凡尼亞州]][[匹兹堡|匹兹堡]]開拍<ref>{{cite web|title=‘The Fault in Our Stars’ filming in Pittsburgh (Filming Locations Open Thread)|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/tag/the-fault-in-our-stars-filming-in-pittsburgh/|publisher=On Location Vacations|accessdate=2014-04-17|date=2013-08-26|archive-date=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721042318/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/tag/the-fault-in-our-stars-filming-in-pittsburgh/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，拍攝地點設定包括{{link-en|奧克蒙特|Oakmont, Pennsylvania}}<ref>{{cite news|last1=Dezayas|first1=Heidi|title='Fault in Our Stars' begins filming at Oakmont home|url=http://triblive.com/neighborhoods/yourallekiskivalley/yourallekiskivalleymore/4604340-74/street-movie-oakmont#axzz39rVqxylw|accessdate=2014-08-09|publisher=triblive.com|date=2014-08-28|archive-date=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721074521/http://triblive.com/neighborhoods/yourallekiskivalley/yourallekiskivalleymore/4604340-74/street-movie-oakmont#axzz39rVqxylw|dead-url=no}}</ref>和{{link-en|UPMC匹兹堡兒童醫院|Children's Hospital of Pittsburgh of UPMC}}及歷史悠久的第五酒店大廈<ref>{{cite news |last=Payne |first=Sara |url=http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/movies/2014/05/07/When-movies-film-in-Pittsburgh-experiences-vary/stories/201405070066 |title=When movies film in Pittsburgh, experiences vary — Pittsburgh Post-Gazette |publisher=Post-gazette.com |date=2014-05-06 |accessdate=2014-05-23 |archive-date=2015-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722044701/http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/movies/2014/05/07/When-movies-film-in-Pittsburgh-experiences-vary/stories/201405070066 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，此歷史景點亦是電影特色之一。教堂的場景是在[[賓夕凡尼亞州|賓夕凡尼亞州]][[匹茲堡|匹茲堡]]郊區{{link-en|黎巴嫩峰|Mt. Lebanon, Pennsylvania}}的聖保羅主教教堂拍攝<ref>{{cite news|last1=Yiin|first1=Wesley|title=Mt. Lebanon church channels Hollywood with 'Fault in Our Stars' screening|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/2014/06/06/Church-channels-Hollywood-with-Fault-screening/stories/201406060103|accessdate=2014-08-09|publisher=post-gazette.com|date=2014-06-06|archive-date=2018-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180625214011/http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/2014/06/06/Church-channels-Hollywood-with-Fault-screening/stories/201406060103|dead-url=no}}</ref>，電影團隊於賓夕凡尼亞州拍攝至10月10日<ref>{{cite news|title=Production Exclusive – Filming Wraps on "The Fault in Our Stars" Movie Adaptation|url=http://trulyluminary.com/2013/10/18/production-exclusive-filming-wraps-on-the-fault-in-our-stars-movie-adaptation/|accessdate=2014-08-09|publisher=trulyluminary.com|date=2013-10-18|archive-date=2014-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810061739/http://trulyluminary.com/2013/10/18/production-exclusive-filming-wraps-on-the-fault-in-our-stars-movie-adaptation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然後拍攝團隊轉到[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]，於10月14日開始繼續拍攝<ref>{{cite news|last1=Christine|title=The Fault In Our Stars moves from Pittsburgh to Amsterdam|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2013/10/15/the-fault-in-our-stars-moves-from-pittsburgh-to-amsterdam/|accessdate=2014-08-09|publisher=onlocationvacations.com|date=2013-10-15|archive-date=2018-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181121021031/https://onlocationvacations.com/2013/10/15/the-fault-in-our-stars-moves-from-pittsburgh-to-amsterdam/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，直至2013年10月16日正式結束<ref>{{cite web|last1=Green|first1=John|title=Last day with my Gus|url=https://twitter.com/realjohngreen/statuses/390568840285155328|publisher=twitter.com|accessdate=2014-08-09|archive-date=2014-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821001139/https://twitter.com/realjohngreen/statuses/390568840285155328|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=West|first=Kelly|title=Shailene Woodley And Ansel Elgort Cozy Up In The Fault In Our Stars Photo|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Shailene-Woodley-Ansel-Elgort-Cozy-Up-Fault-Our-Stars-Photo-40932.html|publisher=Cinema Blend|date=2014-01-03|access-date=2014-06-09|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207182128/https://www.cinemablend.com/new/Shailene-Woodley-Ansel-Elgort-Cozy-Up-Fault-Our-Stars-Photo-40932.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在阿姆斯特丹的時候，拍攝在那裡進行了三天，[[莎蓮·活莉|莎蓮·活莉]]與[[安塞爾·埃爾格特|安索·果特]]坐在河邊的公共長椅上進行拍攝。2014年7月2日，據《[[衛報|衛報]]》的消息透露，拍攝的那張長椅不翼而飛，當地市政府官員也承認他們也不知道它在哪裡，阿姆斯特丹的發言人斯蒂芬·凡得·胡克（Stephan van der Hoek）說：「這真有點讓人尷尬，因為我們對它們有良好的追蹤，但它仍然消失了。」他並承諾將會在數周內重新安裝新的長椅<ref>{{cite news|last1=Beaumont-Thomas|first1=Ben|title=Bench from The Fault in Our Stars goes missing in Amsterdam|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/jul/02/the-fault-in-our-stars-bench-missing-amsterdam|accessdate=2014-08-09|publisher=theguardian.com|date=2014-07-02|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821100958/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/jul/02/the-fault-in-our-stars-bench-missing-amsterdam|dead-url=no}}</ref>。就在一星期後，《娛樂周刊》指阿姆斯特丹電影辦公室曾在推特拍攝重新安裝回被盜長椅的照片；阿姆斯特丹電影專員西蒙·布雷斯特（Simon Brester）說那是同一張長椅，並非替代品<ref>{{cite news|last1=McHenry|first1=Jackson|title=The 'Fault in Our Stars' bench is back in Amsterdam|url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2014/07/07/tfios-bench-amsterdam/|accessdate=2014-09-30|publisher=ew.com|date=2014-07-07|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022113441/http://popwatch.ew.com/2014/07/07/tfios-bench-amsterdam/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在匹兹堡的拍攝亦包括在[[安妮·弗蘭克之家|安妮·弗蘭克之家]]的室內場景，那是在位於匹茲堡東郊的丘吉爾自治市鎮匹茲堡工作室的音樂舞台上重建<ref>丘吉爾自治區總統</ref>，製作設計師莫莉·休斯（Molly Hughes）及藝術總監格雷格·衛文斯（Greg Weimerskirch）在匹茲堡建了三個工作室設置，每層一個<ref>{{cite news | url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/how-the-fault-in-our-stars-recreated-the-anne-frank-house-1201214609/ | work=Variety | first=Ramin | last=Setoodeh | title=How 'The Fault in Our Stars' Recreated the Anne Frank House | date=2014-06-06 | accessdate=2018-02-15 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112021202/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/how-the-fault-in-our-stars-recreated-the-anne-frank-house-1201214609/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，印第安納波利斯的{{link-en|藝術紀念碑|Funky Bones}}在荷蘭藝術家兼雕塑的創作人Joep Van Lieshout的協助下在匹茲堡重新創建<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indystar.com/story/entertainment/movies/2013/08/30/the-fault-in-our-stars-movie-written-here-set-here-shot-where-/2742803/|title='Fault' movie written here, set here, shot where?|date=2013-08-31|work=Indianapolis Star|access-date=2018-02-15|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610200553/https://www.indystar.com/story/entertainment/movies/2013/08/30/the-fault-in-our-stars-movie-written-here-set-here-shot-where-/2742803/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

小說的作者約翰·格林雖是印第安納波利斯的當地人，然而他對選擇於匹茲堡取景拍攝感到滿意。他指：
<blockquote>匹茲堡有一個在過去20年建立起來的真正具才華的電影專業人士的驚人社區，我被他們的專業精神、信心、及他們的奉獻所震懾。沒有很多城市像這般，你必須找到一個可以成為印第安納波利斯的城市。而匹茲堡即使有許多山丘，也可以成為印第安納波利斯。我們只需要找幾條平坦的街道<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pittsburghmagazine.com/Best-of-the-Burgh-Blogs/The-412/October-2013/QA-The-Fault-in-Our-Stars-Author-John-Green/#sthash.CQwZmVIp.dpuf|title=Q+A: 'The Fault in Our Stars' Author John Green|work=pittsburghmagazine.com|access-date=2018-02-15|archive-date=2015-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150814200132/http://www.pittsburghmagazine.com/Best-of-the-Burgh-Blogs/The-412/October-2013/QA-The-Fault-in-Our-Stars-Author-John-Green/#sthash.CQwZmVIp.dpuf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。</blockquote>

