== 票房 ==
《生命中的美好缺憾》的首映禮於2014年6月2日在[[紐約市|紐約市]]的{{link-en|齊格菲爾德劇院|Ziegfeld Theatre (1969)}}舉行，邀請了300位賓客到場欣賞。在首映禮上，作者[[約翰·葛林|約翰·葛林]]說：「我不想把它賣掉，因為荷李活製作關於疾病而不帶情感的電影很糟糕<ref>{{cite news|last1=Setoodeh|first1=Ramin|title=‘The Fault in Our Stars’ Premiere: Even Shailene Woodley Admits to Crying|url=https://variety.com/2014/scene/news/the-fault-in-our-stars-premiere-even-shailene-woodley-admits-to-crying-1201210174/|accessdate=2014-09-23|publisher=variety.com|date=2014-06-03|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202190114/https://variety.com/2014/scene/news/the-fault-in-our-stars-premiere-even-shailene-woodley-admits-to-crying-1201210174/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。電影於2014年6月6日上映<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/books/2013/10/08/john-green-social-media-tfios/2944079/ | title='The Fault In Our Stars' movie gets a release date | work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] | date=2013-10-08 | accessdate=2013-10-10 | last=Deutsch | first=Lindsay | archive-date=2020-11-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115203544/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/books/2013/10/08/john-green-social-media-tfios/2944079/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在紐約的首映後，一名叫伊萬傑琳·厄爾（Evangeline Earl）的學生宣布葛林的電影改編小說是受到其姐姐埃絲特·厄爾（Esther Earl）的啟發，埃絲特也是一名作家。埃絲特患有[[甲狀腺癌|甲狀腺癌]]並於2010年去世。伊萬傑琳指埃絲特曾跟葛林於2009年在[[波士頓|波士頓]]舉行的[[哈利波特|哈利波特]]{{link-en|粉絲聚會|LeakyCon}}中見面，葛林說：「如果我不認識埃絲特，我永遠不會寫得到《生命中的美好缺憾》，書本中的每一個字詞都是取決於她的。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Earl|first1=Evangeline|title=My sister Esther inspired ‘The Fault in Our Stars.’ The movie is her sequel.|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/my-sister-esther-inspired-the-fault-in-our-stars-the-movie-is-her-sequel/2014/06/12/504c2ca4-efef-11e3-914c-1fbd0614e2d4_story.html|accessdate=2014-09-23|publisher=washingtonpost.com|date=2014-06-12|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108171348/https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/my-sister-esther-inspired-the-fault-in-our-stars-the-movie-is-her-sequel/2014/06/12/504c2ca4-efef-11e3-914c-1fbd0614e2d4_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>」葛林指他在小說及電影中使用「好的（okay）」一詞，是因為Hazel及Augustus都用這個字詞來表達他們對彼此的愛，這個字詞成為了他們的特殊詞彙<ref>{{cite web|title=Questions about The Fault in Our Stars (Spoilers!) |url=http://johngreenbooks.com/questions-about-the-fault-in-our-stars-spoilers/ |publisher=johngreenbooks.com |accessdate=2014-09-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141005184550/http://johngreenbooks.com/questions-about-the-fault-in-our-stars-spoilers/ |archivedate=October  5, 2014 }}</ref>。原創小說的靈感來自已故的作者{{link-en|埃絲特·厄爾|Esther Earl}}，她跟她的妹妹阿碧潔爾（Abigail）經常使用「好的（okay）」一詞<ref>{{cite news|last1=Payne|first1=Will|title='I may never get to kiss a boy': Parents of cancer victim, 16, who inspired hit film The Fault in Our Stars reveal she dreamed of a boyfriend just like movie's Gus|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2656487/EXCLUSIVE-Oh-I-never-kiss-boy-Parents-16-year-old-inspired-teen-cancer-victim-Hazel-Grace-A-Fault-Our-Stars-reveal-daughter-dreamed-boyfriend-like-Gus.html|accessdate=2014-09-26|publisher=dailymail.co.uk|date=2014-06-12|location=London|archive-date=2018-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929041501/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2656487/EXCLUSIVE-Oh-I-never-kiss-boy-Parents-16-year-old-inspired-teen-cancer-victim-Hazel-Grace-A-Fault-Our-Stars-reveal-daughter-dreamed-boyfriend-like-Gus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 市場 ===
《生命中的美好缺憾》的首輯電影預告片於2014年1月29日發布，該預告片在少於24小時內已超過3百萬的觀看次數<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.latimes.com/books/jacketcopy/la-et-jc-the-fault-in-our-stars-movie-trailer-book-on-top-20140130,0,3851891.story#axzz2rwahqgXr | title='The Fault in Our Stars' movie trailer hits; the book is on top | work=[[The_Los_Angeles_Times|The Los Angeles Times]] | date=2014-01-30 | accessdate=2014-01-30 | last=Kellogg | first=Carolyn | archive-date=2014-04-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427161557/http://www.latimes.com/books/jacketcopy/la-et-jc-the-fault-in-our-stars-movie-trailer-book-on-top-20140130,0,3851891.story#axzz2rwahqgXr | dead-url=no }}</ref>，在發布首7天內已超過1千5百萬的觀看次數。2014年4月13日，在{{link-en|MTV電影頒獎禮2014|2014 MTV Movie Awards}}節目開始前，電影發布了一個視頻剪輯<ref>{{cite news|last=Wickman|first=Kase|title=This 'Fault In Our Stars' Clip Hits Us Right In The Feelings Bone|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1726041/the-fault-in-our-stars-mtv-movie-awards-exclusive.jhtml|accessdate=2014-04-14|newspaper=mtv.com|date=2014-04-13|archive-date=2014-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416215307/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1726041/the-fault-in-our-stars-mtv-movie-awards-exclusive.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月28日，福克斯發布了一輯擴展預告片，它更透過[[YouTube|YouTube]]發布更多的電影剪輯以作為電影於上映前期推廣的一部分<ref>{{cite news|last1=Strecker|first1=Erin|title=New 'Fault in Our Stars' trailer: More tears, more laughs, more pot?|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/04/28/fault-in-our-stars-trailer/|accessdate=2014-08-29|publisher=ew.com|date=2014-04-28|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022060651/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/04/28/fault-in-our-stars-trailer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

