The Fault in Our Stars Review |author=Simon Miraudo |publisher=Quickflix |date=2014-05-28 |accessdate=2014-06-06 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006145541/http://www.quickflix.com.au/news/reviews/TheFaultinOurStars |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。」《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》的{{link-en|理查德·羅珀|Richard Roeper}}給了此電影四顆星，他說活莉飾演Hazel的表現是「超然、純粹和真實的」，並指「她是那麼難忘<ref>{{cite news|last1=Roeper|first1=Richard|title=‘The Fault in Our Stars’: A lovely work led by the transcendent Shailene Woodley|url=http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/movies/27856994-421/the-fault-in-our-stars-a-lovely-work-led-by-the-transcendent-shailene-woodley.html|accessdate=2014-09-24|publisher=suntimes.com|date=2014-06-04|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024012855/http://www.suntimes.com/entertainment/movies/27856994-421/the-fault-in-our-stars-a-lovely-work-led-by-the-transcendent-shailene-woodley.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》雜誌的斯科特·門德爾森（Scott Mendelson）說這電影是「特別高質量的主流娛樂」，並稱它為「真正的藝術品<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mendelson|first1=Scott|title=Review: Shailene Woodley's 'Fault In Our Stars' Is A Generational Classic|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/06/05/review-shailene-woodleys-fault-in-our-stars-is-a-generational-classic/|accessdate=2014-09-24|publisher=forbes.com|date=2014-06-05|archive-date=2018-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615163610/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2014/06/05/review-shailene-woodleys-fault-in-our-stars-is-a-generational-classic/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》的安娜·史密夫（Anna Smith）說它是「一個感動浪漫和莎蓮·活莉現時為止最佳的表現<ref>{{cite news|last1=Smith|first1=Anna|title=The Fault In Our Stars|url=http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=138467|accessdate=2014-09-25|publisher=empireonline.com|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924135708/http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=138467|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。《[[數碼間諜|數碼間諜]]》的艾瑪·迪